<p>
	Incense can be a natural way to fragrance and purify your atmosphere. With an array of fragrances available to match your mood, there are scents suitable for each room in the home. Incense use doesn&rsquo;t have to be restricted to use only in the relaxing areas of the home, whilst there are many calming and relaxing fragrances available, there are also scents designed to uplift and invigorate.</p>
<p>
	The most common type of incense is used is incense sticks. Incense sticks are lit at the top and then the flame carefully blown out until a slight glow remains. The incense stick then burns and gently fragrances the room with the scent of your choice.</p>
