	Use incense cones as an alternative to incense sticks. The aroma is richer than through using the incense sticks and it is more intense. As inhaling the aroma of incense is believed by some to relieve headaches, it will therefore releive your headache and clear your mind more quickly and promote clarity of thinking.</p>
